## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="90b38-156">Quando il <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> proprietà viene assegnato a un oggetto creato in precedenza <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, il <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> non verrà duplicato.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-156">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> property is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b38-157">Al contrario, il <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> mantiene un riferimento all'oggetto creato in precedenza <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-157">Instead, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="90b38-158">Durante un'operazione di aggiornamento, se <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> non è impostata e chiave primaria sono presenti informazioni nel <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, è possibile utilizzare il <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> (classe) per generare automaticamente il <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>e comandi aggiuntivi necessari per risolvere le differenze tra il <xref:System.Data.DataSet>al database.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-158">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b38-159">A tale scopo, impostare il <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> proprietà del <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-159">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b38-160">La logica di generazione richiede anche informazioni della colonna chiave è presente nel <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-160">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b38-161">Per altre informazioni, vedere [la generazione di comandi tramite commandbuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-161">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="90b38-162">L'esempio seguente crea un' <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> e imposta il <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> e <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> proprietà.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-162">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b38-163">Si presuppone di aver già creato un <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> oggetto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-163">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   
  
  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  Dim parm As OracleParameter  
  
  ' Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd  
  
  ' Create the DeleteCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", conn)  
  
  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original  
  
  da.DeleteCommand = cmd  
  
  Return da  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
{  
  OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter();  
  OracleCommand cmd;  
  OracleParameter parm;  
  
  // Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " +  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn);  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14);  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13);  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd;  
  
  // Create the DeleteCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", conn);  
  
  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original;  
  
  da.DeleteCommand = cmd;  
  
  return da;  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="90b38-166">Quando il <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> proprietà viene assegnato a un oggetto creato in precedenza <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> oggetto, il <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> non verrà duplicato.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-166">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> property is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b38-167">Al contrario, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> mantiene un riferimento all'oggetto creato in precedenza <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-167">Instead, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="90b38-168">Durante un'operazione di aggiornamento, se <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> non è impostata e chiave primaria sono presenti informazioni nel <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, è possibile utilizzare il <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> (classe) per generare automaticamente <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>e comandi aggiuntivi necessari per risolvere le differenze tra il <xref:System.Data.DataSet> nel database.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-168">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b38-169">A tale scopo, impostare il <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> proprietà del <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-169">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b38-170">La logica di generazione richiede anche informazioni della colonna chiave è presente nel <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-170">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b38-171">Per altre informazioni, vedere [la generazione di comandi tramite commandbuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-171">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="90b38-172">Se l'esecuzione di questo comando restituisce le righe, le righe possono essere aggiunte al <xref:System.Data.DataSet> in base al modo in cui si imposta la <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A> proprietà del <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> oggetto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-172">If execution of this command returns rows, these rows may be added to the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> depending upon how you set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="90b38-173">Quando si aggiorna una colonna con il `LONG RAW` tipo di dati, viene generata un'eccezione quando si immette un valore di `NULL` nella colonna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-173">When you update a column with the `LONG RAW` data type, an exception is thrown when you enter a value of `NULL` in the column.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b38-174">Oracle `LONG RAW` tipo di dati è un tipo deprecato in Oracle versione 8.0.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-174">The Oracle `LONG RAW` data type is a deprecated type in Oracle version 8.0.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b38-175">Per evitare questo errore, usare il `BLOB` del tipo di dati anziché `LONG RAW`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-175">To avoid this error, use the `BLOB` data type instead of `LONG RAW`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="90b38-176">L'esempio seguente crea un' <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> e imposta il <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> e <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> proprietà.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-176">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b38-177">Si presuppone di aver già creato un <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> oggetto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b38-177">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  
  
